These pants are comfort in the form of a jogger. Featuring an elastic waistband and a drawstring waist for the perfect, cozy fit. The fabric is super soft and perfect for everyday wear. Plus, the front carpenter and back patch pockets give them added functionality and versatility.
Material: Body- 100% Tencel; Trim- 95% Cotton, 5% Spandex
Lyocell is a biodegradable fabric made from cellulose found in wood pulp. It is softer, more breathable, and uses 10-20 times less water in production compared to cotton.
Wrinkle resistant, shrink resistant, and static resistant
Inseam: 26.375"
Garment-dyed using Azo free dyes to give each garment a vintage one-of-a-kind look
Elastic waistband with metal drawstring tips
Front carpenter and back patch pockets
If you are between sizes, size up on this item
